            "title": "韓國和美國尋求就建造核動力潛艇簽署單獨協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"韓國和美國尋求就建造核動力潛艇簽署單獨協議\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vMChQ0OWU4BzGspLnMGngA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/f0c1d0d0-e137-11f0-b777-ff65e57a338c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">韓國和美國尋求就建造核動力潛艇簽署單獨協議</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
