            "title": "江西銅業擬收購礦企SolGold 交易價值或高達8.67億英鎊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"江西銅業擬收購礦企SolGold 交易價值或高達8.67億英鎊\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6xQaKaAyOLu9Kei476NUFA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/1fd31330-e12d-11f0-afd8-f140eb383b0e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">江西銅業擬收購礦企SolGold 交易價值或高達8.67億英鎊</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
